<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Jared Talbot | Bitcoin, Tech & Simple Systems</title>
  <meta
    name="description"
    content="Jared Talbot builds simple systems that solve real-world problems — from Bitcoin education to practical tech support and digital strategy."
  />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0a0d12;
      --bg-2: #11161d;
      --surface: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      --surface-2: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
      --surface-3: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      --text: #f4f7fb;
      --muted: #b2bfce;
      --line: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      --orange: #ff6a00;
      --orange-2: #ff8b3d;
      --cyan: #4cc9f0;
      --green: #7bd88f;
      --shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      --radius: 24px;
      --max: 1180px;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(255, 106, 0, 0.14), transparent 28%),
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(76, 201, 240, 0.12), transparent 26%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #070a0f 0%, #0a0d12 100%);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .container {
      width: min(100% - 32px, var(--max));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .page {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 100vh;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .glow {
      position: absolute;
      pointer-events: none;
      border-radius: 999px;
      filter: blur(80px);
      opacity: 0.7;
    }

    .glow-1 {
      top: -120px;
      left: -80px;
      width: 280px;
      height: 280px;
      background: rgba(255, 106, 0, 0.18);
    }

    .glow-2 {
      top: 80px;
      right: -80px;
      width: 360px;
      height: 360px;
      background: rgba(76, 201, 240, 0.14);
    }

    .topbar {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 20;
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      background: rgba(10, 13, 18, 0.74);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .topbar-inner {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 20px;
      padding: 18px 0;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .brand-dot {
      width: 12px;
      height: 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--orange), var(--orange-2));
      box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(255, 106, 0, 0.5);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .top-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .top-email {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: 0.2s ease;
    }

    .top-email:hover {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 70px 0 36px;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.14fr 0.86fr;
      gap: 28px;
      align-items: end;
    }

    .hero-card,
    .panel,
    .route-card,
    .trust-card,
    .contact-card {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.05), rgba(255,255,255,0.035));
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .hero-card {
      padding: 34px;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 8px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 106, 0, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 106, 0, 0.15);
      color: #ffd2b2;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 18px 0 14px;
      font-size: clamp(2.7rem, 6vw, 5.1rem);
      line-height: 0.98;
      letter-spacing: -0.06em;
      max-width: 11.5ch;
    }

    .hero-subline {
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      font-size: 1.08rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text);
      max-width: 42ch;
    }

    .hero-copy {
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 720px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 26px;
    }

    .hero-trust {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }

    .hero-trust span {
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78);
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 50px;
      padding: 14px 22px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: 0.2s ease;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--orange), var(--orange-2));
      color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(255, 106, 0, 0.22);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
      border-color: var(--line);
      color: white;
    }

    .panel {
      padding: 28px;
    }

    .panel-label {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
    }

    .panel h2 {
      margin: 10px 0 12px;
      font-size: 2rem;
      line-height: 1.05;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    .panel p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .pill-stack {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 22px;
    }

    .pill {
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.82);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 28px 0 64px;
    }

    .section-head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: end;
      gap: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    .section-head p {
      margin: 0;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .section-head h3 {
      margin: 8px 0 0;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
      line-height: 1.06;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    .section-note {
      max-width: 420px;
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      text-align: right;
    }

    .routes {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 22px;
    }

    .route-card {
      padding: 28px;
      transition: 0.22s ease;
    }

    .route-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.06), rgba(255,255,255,0.045));
    }

    .route-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      padding: 7px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.56);
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .route-card h4 {
      margin: 18px 0 10px;
      font-size: 2rem;
      line-height: 1.05;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    .route-card p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .route-list {
      margin: 18px 0 0;
      padding-left: 18px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.82);
    }

    .route-list li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .route-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }

    .mini-btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 42px;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 700;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      color: white;
      transition: 0.2s ease;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }

    .mini-btn:hover {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }

    .mini-btn.primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--orange), var(--orange-2));
      border-color: transparent;
    }

    .trust-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 22px;
    }

    .trust-card {
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .trust-card h4 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      line-height: 1.08;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .trust-card p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .trust-icon {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 46px;
      height: 46px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .contact-card {
      padding: 28px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
      gap: 22px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .contact-card h3 {
      margin: 8px 0 10px;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
      line-height: 1.08;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    .contact-card p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 720px;
    }

    .contact-links {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .contact-link {
      display: block;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.86);
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: 0.2s ease;
    }

    .contact-link:hover {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    }

    footer {
      padding: 32px 0 44px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.42);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }

    .footer-inner {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      padding-top: 20px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .hero-grid,
      .routes,
      .trust-grid,
      .contact-card {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .section-note {
        text-align: left;
        max-width: none;
      }

      .footer-inner {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .topbar-inner {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      .hero-card,
      .panel,
      .route-card,
      .trust-card,
      .contact-card {
        padding: 22px;
      }

      h1 {
        max-width: none;
      }

      .hero-actions,
      .route-actions {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: stretch;
      }

      .btn,
      .mini-btn,
      .top-email {
        width: 100%;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .section-head {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page">
    <div class="glow glow-1"></div>
    <div class="glow glow-2"></div>

    <header class="topbar">
      <div class="container topbar-inner">
        <div class="brand">
          <span class="brand-dot"></span>
          <span>Jared Talbot</span>
        </div>
        <div class="top-actions">
          <a class="top-email" href="mailto:hello@jaredtalbot.com">hello@jaredtalbot.com</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="container">
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-grid">
          <div class="hero-card">
            <div class="eyebrow">Bitcoin • Tech • Practical Systems</div>
            <h1>I build simple systems that solve real-world problems.</h1>
            <div class="hero-subline">
              From Bitcoin education to hands-on technical support, I help people move forward with clarity.
            </div>
            <p class="hero-copy">
              This is my digital hub — connecting the projects I’m building across Bitcoin,
              practical tech support, and system thinking. If you’re here, the goal is simple:
              choose the right path and move forward.
            </p>

            <div class="hero-actions">
              <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#routes">Choose Your Path</a>
              <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="mailto:hello@jaredtalbot.com">Get in Touch</a>
            </div>

            <div class="hero-trust">
              <span>Built independently</span>
              <span>No noise</span>
              <span>Real solutions</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <aside class="panel">
            <p class="panel-label">How I Work</p>
            <h2>Clear thinking beats complexity.</h2>
            <p>
              I focus on building systems that are simple, effective, and built to last.
              Whether it’s Bitcoin, IT support, or digital infrastructure, the goal is always
              the same: remove confusion, increase control, and create momentum.
            </p>

            <div class="pill-stack">
              <div class="pill">Remove confusion</div>
              <div class="pill">Increase control</div>
              <div class="pill">Create momentum</div>
            </div>
          </aside>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="routes" class="section">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div>
            <p>Choose Your Path</p>
            <h3>Two focused ways I can help</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="section-note">
            If you’re here for Bitcoin, go that way. If you need practical tech help, go that way.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="routes">
          <div class="route-card">
            <span class="route-badge">Bitcoin Education</span>
            <h4>Grow Your BTC</h4>
            <p>
              Bitcoin education and guidance for people who want to secure, understand, and grow
              their BTC the right way.
            </p>
            <ul class="route-list">
              <li>Bitcoin basics and long-term thinking</li>
              <li>Security, self-custody, and setup guidance</li>
              <li>Practical support for building conviction</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="route-actions">
              <a class="mini-btn primary" href="https://growyourbtc.com">Visit Grow Your BTC</a>
              <a class="mini-btn" href="mailto:btc@jaredtalbot.com">Email BTC</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="route-card">
            <span class="route-badge">Local Tech Support</span>
            <h4>Jared Fixes</h4>
            <p>
              Simple, reliable help for everyday tech problems — local support in Wexford plus
              practical remote help where it makes sense.
            </p>
            <ul class="route-list">
              <li>Device setup, troubleshooting, and tech clean-up</li>
              <li>Practical support for security and digital basics</li>
              <li>Simple AI help and clear problem-solving</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="route-actions">
              <a class="mini-btn primary" href="https://jaredfixes.com">Visit Jared Fixes</a>
              <a class="mini-btn" href="mailto:fix@jaredtalbot.com">Email Fix</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div>
            <p>Trust</p>
            <h3>What you can expect</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="section-note">
            A simple approach focused on clarity, usefulness, and real outcomes.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="trust-grid">
          <div class="trust-card">
            <div class="trust-icon">⌁</div>
            <h4>Clear communication</h4>
            <p>
              I prefer plain English, direct thinking, and practical next steps over jargon or unnecessary complexity.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="trust-card">
            <div class="trust-icon">⚙</div>
            <h4>Real-world solutions</h4>
            <p>
              The focus is not theory for its own sake. It’s about solving actual problems and building useful systems.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="trust-card">
            <div class="trust-icon">↗</div>
            <h4>Independent thinking</h4>
            <p>
              I build independently, learn by doing, and care about systems that are trustworthy, resilient, and simple.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <div class="contact-card">
          <div>
            <p class="panel-label">Contact</p>
            <h3>Let’s work together</h3>
            <p>
              If you need help with Bitcoin, tech, or building simple systems that actually work,
              reach out directly. I prefer clear communication and practical next steps.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="contact-links">
            <a class="contact-link" href="mailto:hello@jaredtalbot.com">hello@jaredtalbot.com</a>
            <a class="contact-link" href="mailto:fix@jaredtalbot.com">fix@jaredtalbot.com</a>
            <a class="contact-link" href="mailto:btc@jaredtalbot.com">btc@jaredtalbot.com</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <div class="container footer-inner">
        <span>© 2026 Jared Talbot</span>
        <span>Built independently. No noise. Just real solutions.</span>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
